HEADWORD: Krang
<hw>Krang</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. D. <ets>kreng</ets>
a carcass.]</ety> <def>The carcass of a whale after the blubber has been
removed.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>crang</asp> and
<asp>kreng</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

